ue of John Cory, Cathays Park.jpg|75px]]\n! {{sort|Cory|[[John Cory]]}}\n| Statue\n| Gorsedd Gardens\n| {{sort|1905|1904\u20136}}\n| {{sort|John|Sir [[William Goscombe John]]}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pmsa.cch.kcl.ac.uk/AH/CARDIFF032.htm |title=Statue of John Cory |publisher=Public Monument and Sculpture Association |accessdate=11 March 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101210070346/http://pmsa.cch.kcl.ac.uk/AH/CARDIFF032.htm |archive-date=10 December 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Cathays Park Boer War Memorial.JPG|75px]]\n! [[South African War Memorial, Cardiff|South African War Memorial]]\n| Memorial\n| King Edward VII Avenue\n| {{sort|1907|1905\u20139}}\n| {{sort|Toft|[[Albert Toft]]}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pmsa.cch.kcl.ac.uk/AH/CARDIFF017.htm |title=South African War Memorial |publisher=Public Monument and Sculpture Association |accessdate=11 March 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101208144728/http://pmsa.cch.kcl.ac.uk/AH/CARDIFF017.htm |archive-date=8 December 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Statue of Gwilym Williams, Cathays Park.JPG|75px]]\n! {{sort|Williams|Gwilym Williams}}\n| Statue\n| Outside Cardiff Crown Court\n| {{sort|1908|1906\u201310}}\n| {{sort|John|Sir [[William Goscombe John]]}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pmsa.cch.kcl.ac.uk/AH/CARDIFF016.htm |title=Statue of Judge Gwilym Williams |publisher=Public Monument and Sculpture Association |accessdate=11 March 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100918073710/http://pmsa.cch.kcl.ac.uk/AH/CARDIFF016.htm |archive-date=18 September 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Navigation Glamorgan Building.jpg|75px]]\n! ''Mining''\n| Sculptural group\n| [[Glamorgan Building]]\n| {{sort|1910|1908\u201312}}\n| {{sort|Hodge|[[Albert Hodge]]}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pmsa.cch.kcl.ac.uk/AH/CARDIFF013.htm |title=Naviga