. Returned to The Hayes in September 2019 for another 6 months.\n|<ref>{{cite news|author= |url= |title=Now, what's all this then |work=[[South Wales Echo]] |date=4 May 1972 |page=3 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Laura Clements |url=https://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/cardiff-iron-sculpture-gareth-evans-16938761 |title=This huge iron sculpture is coming back to Cardiff after 47 years |work=[[Wales Online]] |date=18 September 2019 |accessdate=29 September 2019 }}</ref>\n|- \n| [[File:Without Place.jpg|75px]]\n! ''Without Place''\n| Sculpture\n| Junction of Charles Street and Queen Street\n| 2011\n| {{sort|O'Connor Denis|Denis O'Connor and Bernie Rutter}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Waldram|first1=Hannah|title=Question: What do you think of the city's new Charles Street sculpture?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/cardiff/2011/mar/29/cardiff-public-art-charles-street-without-place|work=The Guardian|date=29 March 2011|accessdate=28 November 2014}}{{Self-published source|date=November 2014}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Grangetown==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Image\n! {{nobreak|Title / individual}} commemorated\n! Type\n! Location\n! Date\n! Sculptor\n! {{nobreak|Architect /}} Designer\n! Notes\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Source\n|-\n| [[File:'A Private View' A4232 - geograph-3955220-by-Jaggery.jpg|75px]]\n! ''A Private View''\n| Stainless steel sphere\n| [[A4232 road|A4232 link road]]\n| 1995\n| {{sort|Atherton|Kevin Atherton}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|\n|<ref name=\"CPAR 7\" />\n|-\n|[[File:War memorial, Grange Gardens, Cardiff.jpg|75px]]\n! Grange Gardens War Memorial\n| Memorial with statue\n| Grange Gardens\n| 1920\n| {{sort|Fehr|[[Henry Charles Fehr]]}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|\n|<ref name=\"CPAR 23\">{{cite journal|url=https://www.cardiff.gov.uk/ENG/resident/Planning/Documents/The%20Cardiff%20Public%20Art%20Register.pdf |title=Cardiff Public Art Register |publisher=Cardiff Council |year=2011 |page=23 |a