_2166.htm |title=Connect 4 \u2013 Cardiff |publisher=Detail 360&#176; |accessdate=1 April 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Drinking fountain, Dock Feeder bridge - geograph.org.uk - 1376888.jpg|75px]]\n! Drinking fountain\n| Drinking fountain\n| Dock Feeder\n| 1862\n| {{sort|Wills|W. and T. Wills}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pmsa.cch.kcl.ac.uk/pmsa-database/11390/ |title=Drinking Fountain |publisher=Public Monument and Sculpture Association |accessdate=24 August 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304104150/http://pmsa.cch.kcl.ac.uk/pmsa-database/11390/ |archive-date=4 March 2016 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Jim Driscoll statue, Cardiff.JPG|75px]]\n! {{sort|Driscoll|[[Jim Driscoll]]}}\n| Statue \n| Bute Terrace\n| 1997\n| {{sort|Blacker|[[Philip Blacker]]}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|\n|<ref name=\"CPAR 42\">{{cite journal|url=https://www.cardiff.gov.uk/ENG/resident/Planning/Documents/The%20Cardiff%20Public%20Art%20Register.pdf |title=Cardiff Public Art Register |publisher=Cardiff Council |year=2011 |page=42 |accessdate=25 January 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205093528/https://www.cardiff.gov.uk/ENG/resident/Planning/Documents/The%20Cardiff%20Public%20Art%20Register.pdf |archivedate=5 December 2014 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:The Family sculpture by Robert Thomas, Cardiff Queen Street - geograph.org.uk - 624471.jpg|75px]]\n! ''Family Group''\n| Sculptural group\n| Queen Street\n| 2009\n| {{sort|Thomas|[[Robert Thomas (sculptor)|Robert Thomas]]}}\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|\n|<ref name=\"CPAR 20\">{{cite journal|url=https://www.cardiff.gov.uk/ENG/resident/Planning/Documents/The%20Cardiff%20Public%20Art%20Register.pdf |title=Cardiff Public Art Register |publisher=Cardiff Council |year=2011 |page=20 |accessdate=25 January 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205093528/https://www.cardiff.gov.uk/ENG/resident/Planning/Documents/The%20Cardiff%20Public%20A